OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,FA group of Jersey doctors has launched
OL,7,Fa series of free lifestyle courses to
OL,8,Fimprove public health in the island.
OL,10,FThose with chronic conditions who have
OL,11,Fattended the sessions reported reduced
OL,12,Fblood pressure and improved diabetes
OL,13,Fwith less reliance on prescription
OL,14,Fmedication.
OL,16,FThe lessons teach islanders how to
OL,17,Fmake healthier choices in their diet
OL,18,Fand incorporate exercise into their
OL,19,Fday-to-day lives, while also learning
OL,20,Fabout sleep and stress management.
