OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,FJon Harvey faced a health scare six
OL,7,Fmonths ago when a blood test revealed
OL,8,Fhe had a very high blood pressure, a
OL,9,Ffatty liver, and was prediabetic.
OL,11,FHowever, since eating healthier and
OL,12,Fincorporating small amounts of
OL,13,Fexercise into his daily routine, he
OL,14,Fhas lost four kilograms of weight, and
OL,15,Fno longer has any of these conditions.
OL,17,F"I didn't realise the health impact
OL,18,Fthat ready meals and ultra-processed
OL,19,Ffoods have on the body," Jon said.
