OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,F"Jersey could really lead the way
OL,7,Fgoing forward on offering proactive
OL,8,Fhealth benefits," Jo explained,
OL,9,F"rather than paying to go to the
OL,10,Fdoctor and get a prescription.
OL,12,F"Carry on eating the way you were
OL,13,Feating because that's not going to
OL,14,Fhelp you."
OL,16,F"The food you make is your fuel for
OL,17,Flife - I want to live well as long as
OL,18,Fpossible."
