OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,FWith 50.6% of adults in Jersey obese
OL,7,Fand 90 islanders waiting for weight
OL,8,Floss surgery, unhealthy lifestyles are
OL,9,Fmounting pressure on the island's
OL,10,FHealth Service.
OL,12,FDirector of Lifestyle Medicine Jersey,
OL,13,FLauren Perchard-Rees, says the current
OL,14,Fgrowing rate of chronic disease is
OL,15,F"unaffordable".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
