OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,F"We've been supported by the Jersey
OL,7,FCommunity Foundation and Digital
OL,8,FJersey over the last couple of years
OL,9,Fto deliver our courses, and we're
OL,10,Fworking on an online app at the moment
OL,11,Fthat will be launching soon.
OL,13,F"We would really like to be seen as a
OL,14,Fsystem partner with the government of
OL,15,FJersey."
