OL,3,CHealth improvements for those with
OL,4,Cchronic illness after lifestyle courses
OL,6,FProfessor Peter Bradley, Director of
OL,7,FPublic Health, said in a statement
OL,8,Fthat they have received #4 million of
OL,9,Frecurrent funding to support a
OL,10,F'Prevention First' programme which
OL,11,Fwill offer school-level schemes and
OL,12,Ftargeted family behavioural
OL,13,Finterventions to "make healthier
OL,14,Fchoices easier".
